      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOMMY BELL (3) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with his maiden win, then finished a 5.5 lengths third last start at this track over 400m (23.07). Has placed two times at this track. Good run latest and can go on with it. ESTRADA (2) jumped from a squeeze box but quickly into stride and led until late to place third and beaten 4 lengths (26.69) at Warragul in a T3 RSTW over 460m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Expecting another good run. IMPRESS NEMO (1) is better than last start when fourth (23.27) in a Novice race at this track over 400m. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Cannot be taken lightly. BOSS DELUXE (5) was strongly supported last start but missed the frame when fifth (23.35), beaten 11 lengths.",
